{"tid":2420450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唱《願榮光》街頭歌手噪音煩擾脫罪　事主與警員供詞矛盾","createTime":"2021-02-24T03:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T03:09:43.000Z","uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa219a01ab0bd3776a14f61c63b3a6f9545dbf13","tid":2420450,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"呢條賤種上庭講大話<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指，任職<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>清潔管工</strong></span></span>的事主<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>楊宇</strong></span></span>求與警員的證供存在根本性矛盾，指事主楊宇求並非誠實可靠的證人。<br />\n<br />\n楊早前供稱，憑他的觀察，被告自 12 時開始一直在唱歌，半小時內只是間中停頓 1 至 2 秒，令他感到煩擾。警員則表示，案發當日接到戲院里有關行乞及噪音投訴，於 12 時 27 分至 37 分到場巡查，只見有人在調教結他，並無發出噪音。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%94%B1-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89-%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%E6%AD%8C%E6%89%8B%E5%99%AA%E9%9F%B3%E7%85%A9%E6%93%BE%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA-%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E8%88%87%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E4%BE%9B%E8%A9%9E%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2594%25B1-%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589-%25E8%25A1%2597%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%2599%25AA%25E9%259F%25B3%25E7%2585%25A9%25E6%2593%25BE%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BE%259B%25E8%25A9%259E%25E7%259F%259B%25E7%259B%25BE%2F&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=74fcb408\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2594%25B1-%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589-%25E8%25A1%2597%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%2599%25AA%25E9%259F%25B3%25E7%2585%25A9%25E6%2593%25BE%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BE%259B%25E8%25A9%259E%25E7%259F%259B%25E7%259B%25BE%2F&h=77685c97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht